% Read-only advisory for deterministic checkup command output.

Command: {command}

Deterministic results (do not invent new hard failures):
<payload>
{payload_json}
</payload>

Respond with JSON only:

```json
{
  "status": "ok",
  "findings": [
    {"severity": "warn", "area": "contract_rules", "message": "...", "evidence": "..."}
  ]
}
```

Use status "warned" when findings is non-empty. Do not change pass/fail semantics.
